### ─── Auth ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Registrar usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ada Lovelace",
  "email": "ada@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

###

### Login admin
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "admin1234"
}

###

### Login bibliotecario (LIBRARIAN)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "bibliotecario@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "librarian1234"
}

###

### Login lector (USER)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "lector@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "user1234"
}

###

### Perfil propio
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Books ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Listar libros
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books

###

### Buscar por título, autor o género
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books?search=quijote

###

### Filtrar por género y disponibilidad
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books?genre=Novela&available=true

###

### Paginación
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books?page=1&limit=5

###

### Obtener libro por ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/1

###

### Crear libro (librarian o admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{librarianToken}}

{
  "title": "El Principito",
  "author": "Antoine de Saint-Exupéry",
  "genre": "Fábula",
  "isbn": "978-84-261-3229-7",
  "description": "Un piloto conoce a un pequeño príncipe venido de otro planeta.",
  "publishedYear": 1943,
  "copies": 5
}

###

### Actualizar libro (librarian o admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/books/5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{librarianToken}}

{
  "copies": 10,
  "available": 8
}

###

### Eliminar libro (solo admin)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/books/5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ─── Loans ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Solicitar préstamo (dueDate = automático, 14 días)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bookId": 1
}

###

### Mis préstamos
GET http://localhost:3000/api/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Todos los préstamos (librarian/admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/loans/all
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Filtrar préstamos por estado (ACTIVE | RETURNED | OVERDUE)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/loans/all?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Devolver libro
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/loans/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Reviews ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Ver reseñas de un libro
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/1/reviews

###

### Crear reseña (requiere haber devuelto el libro)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Una obra maestra de la literatura universal."
}

###

### Eliminar mi reseña
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Health ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

